---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Sean Zhang">
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm border border-cream-200">
      <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Hi, I'm <strong>Sean Zhang</strong>. Welcome to Steady State, my personal blog where I write about
        machine learning, system engineering, and whatever interesting topics I stumble upon.
      </p>

      <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed mb-4">
        I believe in learning in public and sharing the journey, not just the destination.
        These posts are a mix of tutorials, deep dives, and notes-to-self that I hope
        others might find useful too.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>
          <span class="text-ink-muted">Email:</span>{' '}
          <a href="mailto:sz@seanzhang.me" class="text-coral hover:underline">sz@seanzhang.me</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="text-ink-muted">Twitter:</span>{' '}
          <a href="https://twitter.com/seeeeaaaannnnnn" class="text-coral hover:underline">@seeeeaaaannnnnn</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="text-ink-muted">GitHub:</span>{' '}
          <a href="https://github.com/seanxwzhang" class="text-coral hover:underline">seanxwzhang</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-4">Subscribe</h2>

      <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">
        You can subscribe to new posts via{' '}
        <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-coral hover:underline">RSS</a> or follow me on
        Twitter for updates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
